      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a mechanical limited-slip differential. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including double-VANOS timing adjustment and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and M-spec dampers, providing excellent lateral grip and feedback. While the exterior shows minor stone chips indicative of spirited use, the mechanical vitals are synchronized for peak performance.",
